Example 4 – Normal Question (customized from Ancillary Services FAQ)
Context: [FAQ on ancillary services permissible activities]
Question: What are permissible activities for ancillary services in IFSC?
Response:
The permissible activities for ancillary services in IFSC are as follows:
1. Legal, Compliance and Secretarial;
2. Auditing Services;
3. Professional & Management Consulting Services;
4. Administration, Assets Management Support Services and Trusteeship Services.
As per IFSCA Circular dated 10.02.2021 read with Circular dated 10.06.2021 and 06.04.2023 on Ancillary services
